<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>ServeHive</title>
  <!-- Google Fonts for a modern look -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #ff5c5c;
      --secondary-color: #ff7878;
      --text-color: #333;
      --bg-color: #fff;
      --header-bg: #fff;
      --transition-speed: 0.3s;
      --shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      --dropdown-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      --nav-gap: 1rem;
    }
    
    /* Global Reset */
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-color);
      background-color: #fafafa;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    /* HEADER */
    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background: var(--header-bg);
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
    }
    /* Left Section: Logo */
    .header-left {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--nav-gap);
    }
    .header-left .logo {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }
    /* Center Navigation */
    .header-center ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--nav-gap);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .header-center ul li {
      position: relative;
    }
    .header-center ul li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text-color);
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
      transition: color var(--transition-speed), border-bottom var(--transition-speed);
    }
    .header-center ul li a:hover {
      color: var(--primary-color);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
    }
    /* Dropdown Content for Center Navigation */
    .header-center ul li .dropdown-content {
      display: none;
      position: absolute;
      top: 120%;
      left: 0;
      background-color: var(--bg-color);
      box-shadow: var(--dropdown-shadow);
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      list-style: none;
      min-width: 200px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: opacity var(--transition-speed);
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 999;
    }
    .header-center ul li .dropdown-content li {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }
    .header-center ul li.dropdown:hover .dropdown-content,
    .header-center ul li.dropdown.active .dropdown-content {
      display: block;
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: auto;
    }
    
    /* Right Navigation */
    .header-right ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--nav-gap);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .header-right ul li {
      position: relative;
    }
    .header-right ul li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text-color);
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
      transition: color var(--transition-speed), border-bottom var(--transition-speed);
    }
    .header-right ul li a:hover {
      color: var(--primary-color);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
    }
    /* Dropdown for Right Navigation (Login Dropdown) */
    .header-right ul li .dropdown-content {
      display: none;
      position: absolute;
      top: 120%;
      right: 0;
      background-color: var(--bg-color);
      box-shadow: var(--dropdown-shadow);
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      list-style: none;
      min-width: 200px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: opacity var(--transition-speed);
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 999;
    }
    .header-right ul li .dropdown-content li {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }
    .header-right ul li.dropdown:hover .dropdown-content,
    .header-right ul li.dropdown.active .dropdown-content {
      display: block;
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: auto;
    }
    
    /* HERO SECTION */
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      background-color: #fafafa;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero blockquote {
      font-style: italic;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    .cta-btn {
      padding: 0.85rem 1.8rem;
      background-color: var(--primary-color);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: background var(--transition-speed);
    }
    .cta-btn:hover {
      background-color: var(--secondary-color);
    }
    
    /* CARDS SECTION */
    .cards-section {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
    .cards-section h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }
    .cards-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card {
      background-color: var(--bg-color);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform var(--transition-speed);
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    .card h4 {
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }
    .card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #555;
    }
    
    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    footer a {
      color: var(--text-color);
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- HEADER -->
  <header>
    <div class="header-left">
      <div class="logo">ServeHive</div>
      <nav class="header-center">
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a href="main-landing.ejs">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li class="dropdown">
            <a href="for-companies.ejs" class="dropdown-toggle">For Companies</a>
            <ul class="dropdown-content">
              <li>Easy project listing & updates.</li>
              <li>AI connects you with the best.</li>
              <li>Secure payments</li>
              <li>Dedicated support</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li class="dropdown">
            <a href="for-freelancers.ejs" class="dropdown-toggle">For Freelancers/Startups</a>
            <ul class="dropdown-content">
              <li>Browse and submit proposals.</li>
              <li>Earn ratings & reviews.</li>
              <li>Invoicing & secure payments</li>
              <li>Manage tasks & deadlines.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li class="dropdown">
            <a href="subscription.ejs" class="dropdown-toggle">Subscription</a>
            <ul class="dropdown-content">
              <li>Free: Basic features</li>
              <li>Pro: Unlimited projects</li>
              <li>Enterprise: Custom integrations</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <nav class="header-right">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="about.ejs">About Us</a></li>
        <li class="dropdown">
          <a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle">Login</a>
          <ul class="dropdown-content">
            <li><a href="/company-login">Company</a></li>
            <li><a href="/freelancer-login">Freelancer/Startup</a></li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>
  
  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Where Businesses and Freelancers Grow Together</h1>
    <p>ServeHive connects companies with top-tier freelance talent, streamlines collaboration, and fuels sustainable growth.</p>
    <blockquote>“Empowering Collaboration, Fueling Innovation.”</blockquote>
    <button class="cta-btn">Get Started for Free</button>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CARDS SECTION: Our Goals & Focus -->
  <section class="cards-section">
    <h2>Our Goals & Focus</h2>
    <div class="cards-container">
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Collaboration & Growth</h4>
        <p>Bridging the gap between businesses and talent to foster mutual success.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Seamless Networking</h4>
        <p>Enabling real connections for sustainable, long-term partnerships.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Reliable Support</h4>
        <p>Providing dedicated assistance from onboarding to advanced queries.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Community Impact</h4>
        <p>Empowering professionals and businesses to build stronger communities.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <p>© 2025 ServeHive. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="#">Terms of Service</a> | 
      <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> | 
      <a href="#">FAQ</a>
    </p>
  </footer>
  
  <!-- JavaScript for Dropdown Toggle -->
  <script>
    const dropdownToggles = document.querySelectorAll('.dropdown-toggle');
    dropdownToggles.forEach(toggle => {
      toggle.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        const parentLi = this.parentElement;
        parentLi.classList.toggle('active');
      });
    });
    
    // Close dropdowns when clicking outside the header
    document.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
      dropdownToggles.forEach(toggle => {
        const parentLi = toggle.parentElement;
        if (!parentLi.contains(e.target)) {
          parentLi.classList.remove('active');
        }
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
